data.description: Wonderful family home! 4 bedrooms, 2 baths, with 2 living spaces. The downstairs boasts a 2nd living space with 2 bedrooms, and bathroom, perfect for an in law suite or teenager suite. Large living space upstairs with open dining room and easy access to the kitchen. Hardwood floors upstairs and renovated kitchen with stainless steel appliances. Refrigerator can convey with property. The kitchen also includes an induction stove. Recessed dimmable lighting. Seller to contribute $1000 to purchaser. New roof in 2023 along with an EV charging station in garage. New hot water heater in 2022. New hvac in 2021. Windows replaced in 2020. Professional pictures coming soon.
